OL,3,CTwo jailed after 'reckless' shootout
OL,4,Cleaves bullet holes in cars
OL,6,FNeighbourhood CCTV cameras recorded
OL,7,Fthe numerous shots as they were fired
OL,8,Fthat night
OL,10,FTwo men have been jailed after a
OL,11,Fshootout with at least 18 gunshots
OL,12,Fwhich was seen and heard on CCTV.
OL,14,FWhat police describe as a "reckless
OL,15,Fexchange of fire" started on Crompton
OL,16,FStreet in Oldham, Greater Manchester,
OL,17,Fat 9:50pm on 15 November 2024.
