OL,3,CTwo jailed after 'reckless' shootout
OL,4,Cleaves bullet holes in cars
OL,6,FAaron Grant, 37, and Daniel Eastmond,
OL,7,F41, were among two groups who shot at
OL,8,Feach other, leaving bullet holes in
OL,9,Fdamaged cars.
OL,11,FIt is believed Grant opened fire on
OL,12,Ftwo men on an electric bike as it rode
OL,13,Falong the street, with security
OL,14,Fcameras capturing the shots as they
OL,15,Frang out.
OL,17,FEastmond then got into the driver's
OL,18,Fside of a blue Audi RSQ3, with Grant
OL,19,Fgetting into the passenger side. The
OL,20,Fcar followed the bike before straying
OL,21,F"deliberately" into its path.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
