OL,3,CTwo jailed after 'reckless' shootout
OL,4,Cleaves bullet holes in cars
OL,6,FThe two sides then exchanged fire,
OL,7,Fwith those on the street hearing 15-18
OL,8,Fgunshots, before the men drove and
OL,9,Frode off.
OL,11,FCars were left with damage, including
OL,12,Fthe Audi that Grant and Eastmond had
OL,13,Fbeen in.
OL,15,FGrant, of no fixed abode, and
OL,16,FEastmond, from Lime Green Rd in
OL,17,FOldham, were both sentenced to 14
OL,18,Fyears and 5 months for possession of a
OL,19,Ffirearm and ammunition with intent to
OL,20,Fendanger life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
