OL,4,Cleaves bullet holes in cars
OL,6,FThe two suspects on the bike have not
OL,7,Fyet been identified.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Rick Castley said:
OL,10,F"The reckless exchange of gunfire
OL,11,Fbetween two groups on Crompton Street
OL,12,Fthat Friday evening, could easily have
OL,13,Fresulted in tragic consequences for
OL,14,Ffamilies and residents going about
OL,15,Ftheir everyday lives.
OL,17,F"We reviewed numerous hours of CCTV
OL,18,Ffootage along with evidence we found
OL,19,Fat the scene, which included bullets
OL,20,Ffound in damaged cars that were caught
OL,21,Fup in the crossfire that evening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
