OL,6,F"The quality of the evidence against
OL,7,FEastmond and Grant was overwhelming,
OL,8,Fincluding the footage showing the
OL,9,Flatter of the two suspects, handling
OL,10,Fwhat appears to be a firearm
OL,11,Fimmediately after the incident."
